%% Data Flow Diagram for odh-model-controller
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Dashboard
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as odh-model-controller<br/>Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Controller as odh-model-controller<br/>Controllers
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Gateway as Gateway API<br/>(openshift-ai-inference)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant NGC as NVIDIA NGC API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ModelReg as Model Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User, ModelReg: Flow 1: InferenceService Deployment (RawDeployment Mode)
    User->>K8sAPI: Create InferenceService CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /mutate-serving-kserve-io-v1beta1-inferenceservice<br/>TLS (service-ca cert)
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutated InferenceService
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Watch event: InferenceService created
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Route, NetworkPolicy,<br/>ServiceMonitor, PodMonitor,<br/>TriggerAuthentication<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    Note right of Controller: Creates storage-config Secret<br/>from data connection secrets

    Note over User, ModelReg: Flow 2: LLMInferenceService Auth Setup (Gateway API)
    User->>K8sAPI: Create LLMInferenceService CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-serving-kserve-io-v1alpha1-llminferenceservice<br/>TLS (service-ca cert)
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validated
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Watch event: LLMInferenceService created
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create AuthPolicy (Gateway-targeted)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create AuthPolicy (HTTPRoute-targeted)
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create EnvoyFilter (Authorino TLS bootstrap)

    Note over User, ModelReg: Flow 3: NIM Account Integration
    User->>K8sAPI: Create NIM Account CR + API key Secret<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Watch event: Account created
    Controller->>NGC: Validate API key & fetch model list<br/>Auth: NGC API Key, TLS 1.2+
    NGC-->>Controller: Model catalog response
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ConfigMap (model list),<br/>Template (ServingRuntime),<br/>Secret (image pull)

    Note over User, ModelReg: Flow 4: Data Connection Secret Aggregation
    User->>K8sAPI: Create Secret (label: opendatahub.io/managed=true)
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Watch event: Secret created
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Read all data connection secrets<br/>in namespace
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create/update storage-config Secret<br/>(aggregated S3 credentials)

    Note over User, ModelReg: Flow 5: External Inference Request
    User->>Router: POST /v1/models/model:predict<br/>HTTPS TLS Edge/Reencrypt
    Router->>Controller: Forward to Predictor Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP or 8443/TCP HTTPS
